ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
SubjectDisposal of a 50% undivided right of ownership of the Fort Témiscamingue National Historic Site of Canada into a trust
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment to dispose of a 50% undivided right of ownership in the federal immovable owned by Her Majesty at the Fort Témiscamingue National Historic Site of Canada, Quebec, into a trust.
